cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.RO 

This paper proposes a novel deep neural network architecture for multi-task reinforcement learning, which involves learning representations from input to RL. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CV (Computer Vision) as they are also related to deep learning and neural networks. Additionally, cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.RO (Robotics) are also possible sub-categories as they involve the use of neural networks in robotics and control tasks.
